column5: Although I'm a day late, all the best wishes to you for your birthday Roy.
Thanks bunches folks. You're all very kind....and younger also.
Happy birthday shorty!    Hope you had a good one.  Nauti.
HAPPY BIRTHDAY ROY!!!!    I will keep in mind that I owe you some birthday spankings when I see ya!   LOL
YESSSSSSSSSSSS God DOES love me!!!!
Consider that your birthday gift! LOL
Well happy b-day roy....man go fishing   especially today...hope ya have a good one    cheers
Happy belated Birthday my friend!
Happy Birthday Roy, have a great day and many more wonderful years to come.
happy birthday Roy!
Happy Black Sunday Roy, Sure hope the weather clears up so you can get a few walleye for the dinner table.   Art
Happy birthday to you , happy birthday to you Happy birthday dear Royyyyyyy. Happy birthday to you!  May today be extra special for you.  Cheers,  Jen
Happy Birthday Roy....
Happy Birthday ya ol' fart!!!.. Hope ya have many more!
Way to go Roy,you made another one.....Here's to hoping you make many many more......TC and all our "Best"........Chuck.....
HAPPY BIRTHDAY ROY  May this day bring you happiness and Joy.. and MANY<MANY MORE  Hugz
5 more yrs and you won't have to pay for a license....  Happy B-day Roy.
Happy B Day Roy,and many more,and may the muskie God,get you one today. Have yourself a great day.  Steve
ya,what everyone else said-happy happy.weather is nice this weekend......FISH!!!
Geez, and there I was yakking away with ya in the wee hours and I didn't even know.  Hope you had a great day bud, and many more in the future...  Maureen

Roy, Happy Birthday brother! I still recount that day heading to Lavigne on a beer run with you... Those Dragon Flies did not stand a chance! I refuse to drive in Quebec since that day...LOL  Have a Happy Birthday brother and give J a huge hug for putting up with you for so many many many many years   Gerritt
happy bday hope its a good one!  cheers!
happy birthday many happy returns
Have a great one Roy!!!!!  Bly
Happy Birthday, poppa smurf!
....Oh my, I can hardly believe it. Well I hope you had a great day Bud.  Happy Birthday, have a great year.
Happy Birthday bud.  One week and I'll buy an Old Milwaukee for ya.
*sniff sniff*I cant believe how our little guy is growing up.Happy to ya bud! Joe
Happy Bday Roy hope ya had a good one
Pouvoir vous attrape un grand, grand Musqué. Yup. Happy birthday my friend.
Have a great day Roy. Meeting up with you in Picton  at the GTG I instantly could tell why you are talked so highly about. It is an honor to know some one like you. Happy birthday.
So o o o ! you've hit the great 60 !!  Happy Birthday Friend, Jackie and I hope you see many more.
Happy Birthday Darlin.  A little birdie told me this is a biggun!!!  You have the best day sweetie.  Joey
Happy Birthday and welcome to the old farts club!!!!
Happy Birthday!!!  Go fishing.....  dk
Damn..........Roy has a biggun?  Happy biggun Roy. Hope you have a great day.
Many more to you Roy.  Enjoy the day.
HAPPY BIRTHDAY ROY!!!!!!!
Joyeux anniversaire Roy, beaucoup plus à venir
Menage a Peche! Roy  Happy b-day
Happy Birthday Roy !!!!!!!
Hey Roy hope you have a great B-Day weekend!!!  Cheers, 1leg
I thought he was already there.LOL  You have the bestest of day me buds.  Bonne fête ! ( i gots that off the interent,hope it,s right.)
Happy day Roy. See you during the first week of August.
All the best, have a good one!
Big and Roy don't go together  Have a great on bud!  Happy Birthday!  Whopper
Best Fishes to you, Roy, mon vieux.
happy birthday have a great one
Happy b-day bud!! May you have a whole heck of a lot more.

Thanks folks. Was wanting to get out on the Larry today but I'm watching the radar and it's still all yellow and orange all around me. It should clear up by tonight. Being 60, I feel ok but I still, for the life of me can't figure out why my father used to refer to my date of birth as "Black Sunday". Have a great day everyone and thank you again.
I hope ya get's a muskie, one inch, for each year of your age . . . . .     geeze . . . . .    he'd be taller'n YOU!! Have a GR R R R  E  A  T one!!
HAPPY BIRTHDAY!!!!!!!!!!!!!!Way to go Roy
Have a great day Roy!!
Happy Birthday neighbor.60 ans vous etes rendu tres vieux  Just don't shrink anymore PAPA Smurf.  Mike
Have a good one Roy and for the Black Sunday isnt that the only day The Black Crapie bite . Peace Ken and thanks for your work on OFC
Have a good one dude!  all the fun you are legally allowed Roy and then some!  Cheers mate!  ID1
Happy Birthday Roy and hope you have many more!
